"title": "1449: signs, purposes of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1449: signs, purposes of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Signs are given to confirm God's word. They may warn the rebellious or encourage the faithful. People may seek signs as a result of a genuine desire to serve God.</p>\n<h2>Signs are given to demonstrate God's power</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:10-Deut34:12\">DEU 34:10–34:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:34\">DEU 4:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:21-Deut6:22\">DEU 6:21–6:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:19\">DEU 7:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:8\">DEU 26:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:11-1Chr16:12\">1CH 16:11–16:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:4-Ps105:5\">PSA 105:4–105:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:21\">JER 32:21</a></p>\n<h2>Signs demonstrate the authority of God's servants</h2>\n<h3>Moses and Aaron</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:1-Exod4:9\">EXO 4:1–4:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:30-Exod4:31\">EXO 4:30–4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:8-Exod7:12\">EXO 7:8–7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num17:1-Num17:9\">NUM 17:1–17:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:36\">ACT 7:36</a></p>\n<h3>Elijah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:36-1Kgs18:38\">1KI 18:36–18:38</a></p>\n<h3>Elisha</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:13-2Kgs2:14\">2KI 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:22\">ACT 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:23\">JHN 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:2\">JHN 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:21\">JHN 7:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:30\">JHN 20:30</a></p>\n<h3>The apostles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:12\">2CO 12:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:43\">ACT 2:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:12\">ACT 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:12\">ACT 15:12</a></p>\n<h3>Signs may accompany the preaching of the gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:3-Heb2:4\">HEB 2:3–2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:20\">MRK 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:6\">ACT 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:3\">ACT 14:3</a></p>\n<h2>Signs may warn the ungodly of impending judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:22-Exod8:23\">EXO 8:22–8:23</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa20:1-Isa20:4\">ISA 20:1–20:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:1-Ezek4:3\">EZK 4:1–4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:3-Ezek12:6\">EZK 12:3–12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:11\">EZK 12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:15-Ezek24:24\">EZK 24:15–24:24</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:29-Jer44:30\">JER 44:29–44:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:34\">LUK 2:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:28\">PHP 1:28</a></p>\n<h2>Signs may warn God's people against rebellion</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num17:10\">NUM 17:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:38\">NUM 16:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num26:10\">NUM 26:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:45-Deut28:46\">DEU 28:45–28:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:34\">1SA 2:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:16-1Sam12:18\">1SA 12:16–12:18</a></p>\n<h2>Signs may encourage faith</h2>\n<h3>By giving guidance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:8-1Sam14:10\">1SA 14:8–14:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:10-Gen24:14\">GEN 24:10–24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:21-Exod13:22\">EXO 13:21–13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:23-2Sam5:24\">2SA 5:23–5:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:14-1Chr14:15\">1CH 14:14–14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:9-Matt2:10\">MAT 2:9–2:10</a></p>\n<h3>By giving assurance of God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:17-Judg6:22\">JDG 6:17–6:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:10-Gen28:17\">GEN 28:10–28:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:1-Exod3:5\">EXO 3:1–3:5</a></p>\n<h3>By encouraging the fearful and doubting</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:7-Isa38:8\">ISA 38:7–38:8</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:8-2Kgs20:11\">2KI 20:8–20:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:24\">2CH 32:24</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:17-Deut7:19\">DEU 7:17–7:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:36-Judg6:40\">JDG 6:36–6:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:15-2Kgs6:17\">2KI 6:15–6:17</a></p>\n<h2>Signs need hold no terror for the godly</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:2\">JER 10:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:6\">MAT 24:6</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:7\">MRK 13:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:9\">LUK 21:9</a></p>\n<h2>Seeking signs</h2>\n<h3>When seeking signs is acceptable to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:11\">ISA 7:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:17\">JDG 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:22\">ISA 38:22</a></p>\n<h3>When seeking signs is condemnned by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:1-Matt16:4\">MAT 16:1–16:4</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:11-Mark8:12\">MRK 8:11–8:12</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:38-Matt12:39\">MAT 12:38–12:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:29\">LUK 11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:16\">LUK 11:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:54-Luke12:56\">LUK 12:54–12:56</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:8\">LUK 23:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:18\">JHN 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:48\">JHN 4:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:30\">JHN 6:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:22\">1CO 1:22</a></p>",
